data.description: Location, location, location! If you are looking for a beautiful, safe community outside of the city, look no further! This lovely 2 story home is located on a corner lot in Blackberry Crossing West subdivision- just 45 miles from downtown Chicago, and in the highly rated Yorkville School District. This home features ample living space- the kitchen has a large island and is completely open to the family room with gas fireplace- both with gorgeous oak hardwood floors that flow from the front entry. Main floor also features a separate dining room, formal living/sitting room and powder room. Upstairs there is a bonus loft area that could make a nice, bright home office/work area. The master bedroom is large, with vaulted ceilings, walk-in closet, and great master bath. The remaining 3 bedrooms are also spacious, and are accompanied by an additional full bath on the 2nd floor. You will be the envy of your family and friends when you host a barbeque out back on the beautiful, recently added (2019) hardscaped patio- complete with LED lighting. There's even a space ready & wired for a hot tub. Recent updates include: Roof- 2021, Carpet on 2nd floor- 2021, LG Smart washer & dryer- 2020, Patio-2019; just to name a few! Attached 2 car garage, nice front porch & fully fenced yard, not to mention easy access to several parks and lots of shopping. You don't want to miss out on this one- set up your private showing today, and you could be in before the holidays!
